body_html:
yes the problem was here
Image directory '/tf_files/flower_photos' not found
I tried to do this:

mkdir tf_files
cd tf_files
curl -O http://download.tensorflow.org/example_images/flower_photos.tgz
tar xzf flower_photos.tgz

it's working!

@microtony @aselle thanks guys!

body:
yes the problem was here 
``` Image directory '/tf_files/flower_photos' not found ```
I tried to do this:
```
mkdir tf_files
cd tf_files
curl -O http://download.tensorflow.org/example_images/flower_photos.tgz
tar xzf flower_photos.tgz
```
it's working!

@microtony @aselle thanks guys!
